  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the thyme, rosemary, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the chestnuts, lemon juice, and pomegranate molasses (if using). Stir to combine.",
    "Add the coconut cream and fermented milk or yogurt. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 30 minutes, or until the chestnuts are tender.",
    "Stir occasionally to prevent scorching.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
